   i   f       (   (   s   e   r   t   x   t   .   i   n   d   e   x   O   f   (   "   '   "   )   &gt;   0   )       |   |       (   s   e   r   t   x   t   .   i   n   d   e   x   O   f   (   "   -   -   "   )   &gt;   0   )       |   |       (   s   e   r   t   x   t   .   i   n   d   e   x   O   f   (   "   ;   "   )   &gt;   0   )           |   |       (   s   e   r   t   x   t   .   i   n   d   e   x   O   f   (   "   (   "   )   &gt;   0   )       |   |       (   s   e   r   t   x   t   .   i   n   d   e   x   O   f   (   "   )   "   )   &gt;   0   )       |   |       (   s   e   r   t   x   t   .   i   n   d   e   x   O   f   (   "   "   )   &gt;   0   )       |   |       (   s   e   r   t   x   t   .   i   n   d   e   x   O   f   (   "   &gt;   "   )   )   &gt;   0       |   |           (   s   e   r   t   x   t   .   i   n   d   e   x   O   f   (   "   #   "   )   )   &gt;   0       )      
   {      
   v   a   r       m   y   s   t   r   i   n   g   =       s   e   r   t   x   t   .   r   e   p   l   a   c   e   (   /   [   \   '   \   -   -   \   ;   \   #   \   \   &gt;   ]   /   g   ,       "   "   )   .   r   e   p   l   a   c   e   (   /   \   (   |   \   )   /   g   ,       "   "   )   ;      
   i   f       (   f   r   o   m   =   =   "   s   e   a   r   c   h   "   )   {   d   o   c   u   m   e   n   t   .   g   e   t   E   l   e   m   e   n   t   B   y   I   d   (   '   q   s   '   )   .   v   a   l   u   e   =   m   y   s   t   r   i   n   g   ;   }   e   l   s   e   {   d   o   c   u   m   e   n   t   .   g   e   t   E   l   e   m   e   n   t   B   y   I   d   (   '   q   '   )   .   v   a   l   u   e   =   m   y   s   t   r   i   n   g   ;   }      
   }      
   }

           w   i   n   d   o   w   .   _   t   a   b   o   o   l   a       =       w   i   n   d   o   w   .   _   t   a   b   o   o   l   a       |   |       [   ]   ;
